info.description:
# colorbox

Color box provides various colors‘ rgb decimal code.

## Usage

```python
>>> from colorbox import rgb, bgr, hex
>>> rgb("red")
(255, 0, 0)
>>> bgr("red")
(0, 0, 255)
>>> hex("red")
'#FF0000'
```
